      "text": "Contents\n© 2017 Potomac Economics 2016 State of the Market Report | i \n/\n2024 STATE OF THE MARKET REPORT\nFOR THE MISO ELECTRICITY MARKETS\nPrepared By: \nIndependent Market Monitor \nfor the Midcontinent ISO \nJune 2025 \n\nContents\n© 2025 Potomac Economics 2024 State of the Market Report \n/\nTABLE OF CONTENTS\nEXECUTIVE SUMMARY ........................................................................................................................... I\nI. INTRODUCTION ............................................................................................................................ 1\nII. PRICE AND LOAD TRENDS ........................................................................................................... 3\nA. Market Prices in 2024 ....................................................................................................... 3\nB. Fuel Prices and Energy Production ................................................................................... 6\nC. Load and Weathe",
